<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent7d547e8efeb346b08184957bc2b4d792">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="BMI The Droitwich Hospital" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=115901"/>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<p><strong>BMI The Droitwich Spa Hospital Worcestershire</strong></p>
</div>
<p><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-droitwich-spa-hospital" target="_blank" title="BMI The Droitwich Spa Hospital">BMI The Droitwich Spa Hospital</a> has 36 beds plus a 10-bedded short stay unit, three theatres, an endoscopy suite and a high dependency unit.</p>
<p>We also treat NHS funded patients and patients who wish to pay for their own treatment. To see which treatments are available for NHS funded patients, please look at the NHS Patients page.</p>
<p>Here is a list of some of the treatments available at <strong>BMI The Droitwich Spa Hospital</strong>:</p>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-droitwich-spa-hospital/orthopaedic-centre" target="_blank" title="Private Orthopaedic Centre in Worcestershire">Private Orthopaedic Centre in Worcestershire</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Arthroscopy for shoulder, elbow or wrist</li>
<li>Carpal Tunnel Syndrome </li>
<li>Shoulder replacement surgery</li>
<li>Arthroscopy for ankle, knee and hip </li>
<li>ACL reconstruction surgery</li>
<li><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-droitwich-spa-hospital/physiotherapy" target="_blank" title="Physiotherapy in Worcestershire">Physiotherapy</a></li>
<li>Spinal surgery</li>
</ul>
<div>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-droitwich-spa-hospital/podiatry-clinic" target="_blank" title="Podiatry Clinic in Worcestershire">Podiatry Clinic in Worcestershire</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Chiropody</li>
<li>Nail surgery</li>
<li>Orthotics </li>
<li>Ankle and knee brace manufacture</li>
<li>3D foot scan</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/treatments/cancer-care" target="_blank" title="Private Oncology Treatment in Worcestershire">Private Oncology Treatment in Worcestershire</a></strong><strong> </strong></div>
<ul>
<li>Hormone therapy</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-droitwich-spa-hospital/diagnostics-and-imaging" target="_blank" title="Private Diagnostics and Imaging Treatment in Worcestershire">Private Diagnostics and Imaging Treatment in Worcestershire</a></strong><strong> </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>CT Scan</li>
<li>MRI </li>
<li>Ultrasound<strong> </strong></li>
<li>X-ray<strong> </strong></li>
</ul>
<div>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-droitwich-spa-hospital/muscle-and-nerve-centre" target="_blank" title="Muscle and Nerve Centre in Worcestershire">Muscle and Nerve Cenre in Worcestershire</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Neurological services </li>
</ul>
</div>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/treatments/cosmetic-surgery" target="_blank" title="Cosmetic Surgery in Worcestershire">Cosmetic Surgery Treatment in Worcestershire</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Cosmetic surgery</li>
<li>Vascular surgery (incl. varicose vein removal)</li>
</ul>
<p>BMI Healthcare offer the best <a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/patient-information/quality-of-care" target="_blank" title="Quality of care">quality of care</a> and services. For more information about our hospitals and service please visit the <a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/" target="_blank" title="BMI Healthcare">website</a>.</p></div>
</div>
