<h4 id="Article-51683">Making healthcare affordable - paying for yourself</h4>
<div id="imageContent16437ea020cd474c88d0c003b688b771">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Paying for yourself" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_ArticleListModule_ArticlesRepeater_ctl00_ctl00_ArticleImage_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=36769"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>Long waiting list for your knee diagnosis or treatment? Don’t miss doing what you love - get fast<br/>private hospital treatment with BMI Healthcare. And now you can spread the cost of your treatment <br/>to suit you with our unique credit card, the BMI Card.  <a href="http://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/paying-for-yourself-0001" target="_blank">Click here to find out more.</a></p>
<p class="last-updated">Last updated on 24 November 2015.</p>
